                     <tr>
                        <td width="24"></td>
                        <td colspan="7" valign="top" width="392">Provisions:</td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">1.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">The funds appropriated in Schedule (1) shall be used for the Funding Agricultural Replacement Measures for Emission Reductions
