                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">2.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">Not more than 5 percent of the amounts appropriated in this item may be used for administrative costs. The funds in this item
                           shall be available for encumbrance or expenditure until June 30, 2027, and shall be available for liquidation until June 30,
                           2029.
                        </td>
                        <td align="right" valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>3.</i></font></td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>The
                           					 Administrative Procedure Act (Chapter 3.5 (commencing with Section 11340) of Part 1 of Division 3 of Title 2 of the
                           Government Code) does not apply to guidelines or other standards adopted and used in administering the funds appropriated
                           in this item.</i></font>
                        </td>
