                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">1.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Notwithstanding any other law, the Department of Finance may authorize the transfer of expenditure authority between Schedules
                              (1) and (2) of this item and between this item and Items 4260-102-0890, 4260-106-0890, 4260-111-0890, 4260-114-0890, and 4260-117-0890
                              in order to effectively administer the programs funded in these
