                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">(c) Chapter 994 of the Statutes of 2024 (Assembly Bill No. 157).</div>
                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">(d) Chapter 995 of the Statutes of 2024 (Assembly Bill No. 180).</div><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>
